gues, and deepen the understanding of each other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2597080/extras/86ef39d4aecf2bdc087f0a429476ecf8.poster.avif?t=1766127040\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2597080/extras/86ef39d4aecf2bdc087f0a429476ecf8.webm?t=1766127040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2597080/extras/86ef39d4aecf2bdc087f0a429476ecf8.mp4?t=1766127040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
